# {{.ProjectName}}

## Project Overview

{{.Description}}

This is a Vue 3 application using the Composition API with TypeScript.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Vue 3 (Composition API)
- **Build Tool**: Vite 6
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4
- **Routing**: Vue Router 4
- **Testing**: Vitest + Vue Test Utils

## Commands

```bash
make dev          # Run Vite dev server
make start        # Start Docker Compose stack
make stop         # Stop Docker Compose stack
make build        # Production build
make test         # Run tests
make lint         # Run linter
make format       # Format code
```

## Project Structure

- `src/main.ts` - Application entry point
- `src/App.vue` - Root component
- `src/views/` - Page-level route components
- `src/components/` - Reusable UI components
- `src/composables/` - Composition API composables (shared logic)
- `src/router/` - Vue Router configuration
- `src/types/` - TypeScript type definitions
- `tests/` - Test files
